						               													<description>Spight is a ball stacking and connection game that can be played with a Series: Shibumi set. It uses a board of 4x4 holes, 8 white balls and 8 black balls.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Setup:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Place 8 black balls and 8 white balls according to the figure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#139;&amp;ensp;&amp;#226;&amp;#151;&amp;#143;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Two players, White and Black, alternate turns moving a ball of their colour either:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;a) jumping like a chess knight from a hole to another empty hole or...&amp;#10;b) jumping up from a hole to an adjacent 2x2 platform or...&amp;#10;c) passing if there are no available moves.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Notice that other balls may drop as a result.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Aim:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Win by connecting all your pieces into a single group.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules for this game are included in the soft cover Shibumi Rule Book&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
